      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine<strong> </strong>your<strong> red wine vinegar</strong>, <strong>mayo</strong>, <strong>remaining sliced spring onion</strong>, 2 tbsp [3 tbsp] <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>in a bowl – this is your<strong> salad dressing</strong></p><p>Slice your <strong>apple[s]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span></strong>(skin on) thinly, discard the core then add to the salad dressing and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>dressed apple</strong></p>",
